  "title": "Operations Assistant | Landscape Project | Bedok Office",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Role: Operations Officer / Assistant [ Landscaping Project ]</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5.5 Work Day, 8am - 5pm / 8am - 12pm</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Salary: $2,500 - $3,200 + Bonus</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>This role will station at Bedok Office, Singapore</strong></p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>QUALIFICATION AND CRITERIA</strong></p><ol><li><p>Interest in managing landscaping projects.</p></li><li><p><u><em><strong> At least 1 year in scheduling and operations management [ manpower management and logistics arrangement ]</strong></em></u></p></li><li><p>Requires to have Class 3 license, will work in a team and travel around both offices in Tengah [ Site Office ] and Bedok [ Headquarter] .<br /></p></li></ol><p>ROLE AND RESPONSIBILITIES</p><ul><li><p>Work closely with the operations team to manage manpower deployment across clusters islandwide.</p></li><li><p>Plan and schedule daily jobs using the company’s system to ensure timely and efficient execution.</p></li><li><p>Lead, motivate, and train team members, fostering professionalism and strong work ethics.</p></li><li><p>Troubleshoot operational challenges and step in when manpower shortages occur.</p></li><li><p>Manage and resolve disciplinary, safety, and operational issues.</p></li><li><p>Participate in recruitment and onboarding of operations team members.</p></li><li><p>Supervise operations to ensure compliance with company procedures and SOPs.</p></li><li><p>Leverage strong knowledge of Singapore roads to optimize logistics and job assignments.</p></li><li><p>Willing to work overtime (OT) when required.</p></li><li><p>Share a genuine passion for plants and contribute positively to the company’s horticultural mission.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
